snippet.title: METAVOIDAL Publisher Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
We are proud to announce that we have partnered with Astrolabe Games to bring Metavoidal to a global audience!

This announcement goes hand-in-hand with Metavoidal's presence at BitSummit 2023 as our debut international appearance. We're so stocked that not only will the English speaking side of the world have the opportunity to play our game, but the Asian Market and beyond!

Stay tuned for what we have in-store for you coming soon. 

Wishlist on our Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2221780/Metavoidal/

Keep up to date with all the MV news here:
Twitter - https://twitter.com/YellowLabGames
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/yellowlabgames/
TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@yellowlabgames
